 leaf=\"\">官方给的例子</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 19.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(198, 110, 73);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的看法</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在「心理健康」相关话题上，「好的响应」是个复杂&amp;重要的问题</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">对此，OpenAI 在对应的「Model Spec」里面，更新了模型应该「支持用户的真实世界关系」、「避免强化可能与心理困扰相关的无根据信念」等条目</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"237\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYr7mokbia9yBIC9qyCzIXlXFibJvSgCBF7vAaTa9Hb86CFXuDC4tXEibicsAIJHQ96iaibhYQ2bUJoh1O7Q/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-imgfileid=\"100023940\" data-ratio=\"0.4348355663824604\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;border-style:solid;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;text-align:left;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;margin:0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1642\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f1415b7e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYr7mokbia9yBIC9qyCzIXlXFibJvSgCBF7vAaTa9Hb86CFXuDC4tXEibicsAIJHQ96iaibhYQ2bUJoh1O7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://model-spec.openai.com/2025-10-27.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://model-spec.openai.com/2025-10-27.html</a></span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些原则，可能会成为所有模型发布的基准安全测试，并持续更新</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但...写到这，我突然汗毛立了一下</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 16px;margin:0px 8px 32px;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 4px 6px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">大模型，如果被利用的话，甚至可以成为舆论战、心理战、乃至意识形态之战的武器...</span><span leaf=\"\">甚至...&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 也可以被成为赛博邪教</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">细思极恐...</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型主权，刻不容缓</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "ChatGPT 内置模型 gpt-5-oct-3 更新，通过引入全球专家网络，显著提升了处理心理健康相关问题的安全性，并优化了长对话的稳定表现。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "ChatGPT 内置模型 gpt-5-oct-3 更新，通过引入全球专家网络，显著提升了处理心理健康相关问题的安全性，并优化了长对话的稳定表现。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了 ChatGPT 内置模型 gpt-5-oct-3 的更新，该版本主要针对心理健康相关问题进行了改进，包括精神病/躁狂、自杀/自残和情感依赖三大敏感领域，不良响应减少了 65-80%。新模型在长对话中也保持了 95%以上的安全性。OpenAI 为此建立了由近 300 位医生和心理学家组成的全球专家网络，并制定了“定义问题-测量-专家验证-降低风险-持续迭代”的五步流程来确保模型安全。文章通过具体案例说明了新模型如何避免强化不健康的心理依赖，并强调了 OpenAI 在 Model Spec 中更新了关于“支持真实世界关系”和“避免强化无根据信念”的原则。作者最后提出对“模型主权”的思考，警示 AI 被滥用为舆论战或“赛博邪教”的潜在风险。",
